                    <span>this is one of the best books if you ever wanted to know anything about databases. I think this isn't a tutorial book or a book for self study on this topic for beginners - but if you ever need to look up for an profound explication on some database matter this will be the book for you.
<br />
<br />This gives you insights into your database, if you are on the frontier from application developer that has to understand what a database realy does.</span>
                  
