                    <span>Be brave. If you can read through this book cover to cover without utter frustration and/or thoughts of complete hopelessness... Than you, sir, are a better man than I.<p>This book was not what I was looking for. I thought I would be intrigued and genuinely interested in reading database theory and its application; Instead I was scared away. The flow of this book is about as high and dry as stale crackers. You chew and chew and chew, and swallow with the eagerness of a pet refusing to take its medicine.</span>
                  
              
